{"id": "cyberhygiene-de-basis-van-digitale-veiligheid__a2-late-chunking__0001", "text": "[Cybersecurity](https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/veilig/index.html)", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "cyberhygiene-de-basis-van-digitale-veiligheid__a2-late-chunking__0001", "source_slug": "cyberhygiene-de-basis-van-digitale-veiligheid", "source_title": "Cyber ​​hygiene: the basis of digital security", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/beveiliging/cyberhygiene-de-basis-van-digitale-veiligheid.html", "source_date": "2025-11-03", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "beveiliging", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 1, "n_chunks_total": 14, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 1}}
{"id": "cyberhygiene-de-basis-van-digitale-veiligheid__a2-late-chunking__0002", "text": "The European NIS2 guideline mentions it nine times: cyber hygiene. That's telling. It is not an option, but an absolute condition for working digitally safely. Entrepreneurs who take cyber hygiene seriously reduce the risk of cyber attacks and lay a strong foundation for sustainable digital resilience.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "cyberhygiene-de-basis-van-digitale-veiligheid__a2-late-chunking__0002", "source_slug": "cyberhygiene-de-basis-van-digitale-veiligheid", "source_title": "Cyber ​​hygiene: the basis of digital security", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/beveiliging/cyberhygiene-de-basis-van-digitale-veiligheid.html", "source_date": "2025-11-03", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "beveiliging", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 2, "n_chunks_total": 14, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 2}}
{"id": "cyberhygiene-de-basis-van-digitale-veiligheid__a2-late-chunking__0003", "text": "Cyber ​​hygiene revolves around the basic measures that every organization must have in place: strong passwords, multi-factor authentication, regular updates, reliable backups and employee alertness. But it is also about daily habits. Consider immediately reporting suspicious emails, locking your screen when you walk away or avoiding private devices without security.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "cyberhygiene-de-basis-van-digitale-veiligheid__a2-late-chunking__0003", "source_slug": "cyberhygiene-de-basis-van-digitale-veiligheid", "source_title": "Cyber ​​hygiene: the basis of digital security", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/beveiliging/cyberhygiene-de-basis-van-digitale-veiligheid.html", "source_date": "2025-11-03", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "beveiliging", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 3, "n_chunks_total": 14, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 3}}
{"id": "cyberhygiene-de-basis-van-digitale-veiligheid__a2-late-chunking__0004", "text": "Yet in practice it appears that many organizations make mistakes. Updates are postponed because production is not allowed to stand still, trainees are given too much access or backups are made but not tested. Old accounts of former employees sometimes remain active. People often think: “We are not interesting for hackers.”", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "cyberhygiene-de-basis-van-digitale-veiligheid__a2-late-chunking__0004", "source_slug": "cyberhygiene-de-basis-van-digitale-veiligheid", "source_title": "Cyber ​​hygiene: the basis of digital security", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/beveiliging/cyberhygiene-de-basis-van-digitale-veiligheid.html", "source_date": "2025-11-03", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "beveiliging", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 4, "n_chunks_total": 14, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 4}}
{"id": "cyberhygiene-de-basis-van-digitale-veiligheid__a2-late-chunking__0005", "text": "Cyber criminals focus on companies that do not have the basics in order. A forgotten update or a weak password is often enough to get in. And once inside, one infected laptop can shut down an entire organization.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "cyberhygiene-de-basis-van-digitale-veiligheid__a2-late-chunking__0005", "source_slug": "cyberhygiene-de-basis-van-digitale-veiligheid", "source_title": "Cyber ​​hygiene: the basis of digital security", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/beveiliging/cyberhygiene-de-basis-van-digitale-veiligheid.html", "source_date": "2025-11-03", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "beveiliging", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 5, "n_chunks_total": 14, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 5}}
{"id": "cyberhygiene-de-basis-van-digitale-veiligheid__a2-late-chunking__0006", "text": "With the NIS2 Quality Mark (NIS2 QM) you show that your organization has properly arranged the basics. The quality mark confirms that you meet the requirements of good cyber hygiene, checked by an independent audit.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "cyberhygiene-de-basis-van-digitale-veiligheid__a2-late-chunking__0006", "source_slug": "cyberhygiene-de-basis-van-digitale-veiligheid", "source_title": "Cyber ​​hygiene: the basis of digital security", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/beveiliging/cyberhygiene-de-basis-van-digitale-veiligheid.html", "source_date": "2025-11-03", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "beveiliging", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 6, "n_chunks_total": 14, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 6}}
{"id": "cyberhygiene-de-basis-van-digitale-veiligheid__a2-late-chunking__0007", "text": "The basis of NIS2 QM consists of 15 measures. For comparison: the international standard ISO 27001 contains 93. For many SMEs, those 15 steps already offer more than enough protection to no longer be of interest to cyber criminals.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "cyberhygiene-de-basis-van-digitale-veiligheid__a2-late-chunking__0007", "source_slug": "cyberhygiene-de-basis-van-digitale-veiligheid", "source_title": "Cyber ​​hygiene: the basis of digital security", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/beveiliging/cyberhygiene-de-basis-van-digitale-veiligheid.html", "source_date": "2025-11-03", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "beveiliging", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 7, "n_chunks_total": 14, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 7}}
{"id": "cyberhygiene-de-basis-van-digitale-veiligheid__a2-late-chunking__0008", "text": "True digital resilience starts with the basics. Anyone who takes cyber hygiene seriously lays the foundation for sustainable security.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "cyberhygiene-de-basis-van-digitale-veiligheid__a2-late-chunking__0008", "source_slug": "cyberhygiene-de-basis-van-digitale-veiligheid", "source_title": "Cyber ​​hygiene: the basis of digital security", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/beveiliging/cyberhygiene-de-basis-van-digitale-veiligheid.html", "source_date": "2025-11-03", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "beveiliging", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 8, "n_chunks_total": 14, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 8}}
{"id": "cyberhygiene-de-basis-van-digitale-veiligheid__a2-late-chunking__0009", "text": "This article was produced in collaboration with [Samen Digitaal Veilig](https://www.samendigitaalveilig.nl/).", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "cyberhygiene-de-basis-van-digitale-veiligheid__a2-late-chunking__0009", "source_slug": "cyberhygiene-de-basis-van-digitale-veiligheid", "source_title": "Cyber ​​hygiene: the basis of digital security", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/beveiliging/cyberhygiene-de-basis-van-digitale-veiligheid.html", "source_date": "2025-11-03", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "beveiliging", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 9, "n_chunks_total": 14, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 9}}
{"id": "cyberhygiene-de-basis-van-digitale-veiligheid__a2-late-chunking__0010", "text": "About 1 in 5 entrepreneurs is confronted with cybercrime. Such a cyber incident can have major consequences for business operations, customers, suppliers or reputation. Taking appropriate measures is therefore important for every company.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "cyberhygiene-de-basis-van-digitale-veiligheid__a2-late-chunking__0010", "source_slug": "cyberhygiene-de-basis-van-digitale-veiligheid", "source_title": "Cyber ​​hygiene: the basis of digital security", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/beveiliging/cyberhygiene-de-basis-van-digitale-veiligheid.html", "source_date": "2025-11-03", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "beveiliging", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 10, "n_chunks_total": 14, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 10}}
{"id": "cyberhygiene-de-basis-van-digitale-veiligheid__a2-late-chunking__0011", "text": "- Do you have an SME company and do you want to reduce your cyber risks? Then take a look at [Cyber ​​Fundament](https://doorpassen.abnamro.nl/producten-en-diensten/cyber-voor-het-mkb/), especially for SME entrepreneurs.\n- Learn more about the 4-in-1 cyber solution [Cyber ​​Safe & Secure](https://doorpassen.abnamro.nl/producten-en-diensten/cyber-veilig-en-zeker/?icmp=cm-od_article-insights_btn-link) especially for large businesses and reduce your cyber risks.\n- Do you also want to [do business safely](https://doorpassen.abnamro.nl/producten-en-diensten/veilig-ondernemen/?icmp=cm-od_article-insights_btn-link)? View smart tools, useful articles and cyber webinars.\n- [Report fraud to us](https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/prive/abnamro/veilig-banken/fraude-melden.html \"Report fraud\"), even if in doubt, after which our helpdesk will help you immediately.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "cyberhygiene-de-basis-van-digitale-veiligheid__a2-late-chunking__0011", "source_slug": "cyberhygiene-de-basis-van-digitale-veiligheid", "source_title": "Cyber ​​hygiene: the basis of digital security", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/beveiliging/cyberhygiene-de-basis-van-digitale-veiligheid.html", "source_date": "2025-11-03", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "beveiliging", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 11, "n_chunks_total": 14, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 11}}
